      • deploymentMethod

        public EthereumContractInfoBuilder.EthereumMethodInfoBuilder deploymentMethod​(java.lang.reflect.Method method)
        Specifies a method as deployment method, i.e. a method that is meant to invoke the smart contract's constructor.

        This method is a shortcut for calling EthereumMethodInfoBuilder.method(method).name(Constants.DEPLOYMENT_METHOD).specialMethod(true)
        Parameters:
        method - method of the smart contract interface
        Returns:
        EthereumContractInfoBuilder.EthereumMethodInfoBuilder for the given method.

      • deploymentMethod

        public EthereumContractInfoBuilder.EthereumMethodInfoBuilder deploymentMethod​(java.lang.String methodName,
                                                                              java.lang.Class<?>... parameterTypes)
        Specifies a method as deployment method, i.e. a method that is meant to invoke the smart contract's constructor.

        This method is a shortcut for calling EthereumMethodInfoBuilder.method(methodName, parameterTypes).name(Constants.DEPLOYMENT_METHOD).specialMethod(true)
        Parameters:
        methodName - name of the method
        parameterTypes - types of the method parameters
        Returns:
        EthereumContractInfoBuilder.EthereumMethodInfoBuilder for the given method.
